OL,5, Washing clothes and letting pupils use 
OL,6, shower facilities are just some of the 
OL,7, ways that schools are trying to address
OL,8, the cost of living pressures that can  
OL,9, keep children away from lessons.       
OL,11,FAttendance is already down about 4% on 
OL,12,Fpre-Covid levels - equating to         
OL,13,Fthousands of hours of missed learning. 
OL,15,FThe cost of living pressures have now  
OL,16,F"exacerbated" these issues.            
OL,18,FAt Henry Tudor School, the team from   
OL,19,FPembrokeshire council support families 
OL,20,Fto get pupils back into class.         
